e><space><space><space><space><space><space>if<space>r<apos>https:<solidus><solidus>raw.githubusercontent.com<solidus>federal-geospatial-platform<solidus>fgp-metadata-proxy<solidus>master<solidus>images<apos><space>in<space>value:<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>self.pyoutput<openparen>feature<closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space>def<space>close<openparen>self<closeparen>:<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>pass }    PY_OUTPUT_TAGS { PYOUTPUT <Rejected> }    OUTPUT { PYOUTPUT FEATURE_TYPE PythonCaller_OUTPUT         }    OUTPUT { <Rejected> FEATURE_TYPE PythonCaller_<Rejected>         }
